messages.messageBody:
Ye all,
the block of rooms at the special show rate is now sold out ( I found
out the hard way ). Book your room asap before the " reasonable " rate
of 129 is gone too................ there's always the presidential
suite at 159 + and above.

The show organiser is looking into the near by Marriott's but then it
means comutting between hotels which is a hassle.

milt

messages.subject: chicago show
messages.msgSnippet: gang, the chicago shinsa show is coming up hot and heavy next week. As the  local yokel  ( as one listero fondly called me ) , I strongely suggest you do not
messages.messageBody:
gang,
the chicago shinsa show is coming up hot and heavy next week.

As the " local yokel " ( as one listero fondly called me ) , I
strongely suggest you do not fly in to Midway airport .
O'hare Airport is where the hotel shuttle bus runs.


South side of Chicago is considered " edgy ".

milt
